OL,3,CMoffat Post Office set to re-open
OL,4,Cfollowing closure in February
OL,6,FMoffat Post Office is set to re-open
OL,7,Ffollowing its closure in February.
OL,9,FThe branch on Station Road closed
OL,10,FThursday 26 February when the previous
OL,11,Fowner sold the business and is now set
OL,12,Fto open on Wednesday 22 April.
OL,14,FSam Williams, Post Office Divisional
OL,15,FRetail Change Manager, said: "We know
OL,16,Fhow important a Post Office is to this
OL,17,Fcommunity and we wanted to restore
OL,18,Fservice as soon as possible,
OL,19,Fespecially as we recognise the
OL,20,Fdistance to the nearest branch.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/2
